This uses sendgrid and python3
Install python3 and pip
then
pip install sendgrid
pip install daemonize

1. Copy motion.service to /etc/systemd/system
2. Install the service sudo systemctl enable motion.service
3. Start the service  sudo systemctl start motion.service
4. See if the service is running ps auxxx | grep motion
   if you don't see motion.py then tail /var/log/syslog
   and fix any errors.
5. If you change motion.service then reload it with sudo systemctl daemon-reload
6. Goto 3 and repeat till its running



Other commands

You can also use systemctl commands like status,
stop, and restart to manage the daemon as a system service.





